<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Mening Kabinetim / Dashboard</title>
  <style>
    /* Avvalgi CSS uslublari */
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a11cb, #2575fc);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      margin: 0;
    }

    .container {
      background: #fff;
      padding: 30px 40px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
      width: 450px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      color: #333;
    }

    .profile-info {
        text-align: left;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding: 15px;
        border: 1px solid #eee;
        border-radius: 8px;
        background: #f9f9f9;
    }

    .profile-info p {
        margin: 8px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #555;
        border-bottom: 1px dashed #eee;
        padding-bottom: 5px;
    }
    
    .profile-info p:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
        padding-bottom: 0;
    }

    .profile-info strong {
        color: #333;
        display: inline-block;
        width: 120px;
    }

    .action-buttons {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    
    .action-buttons a, .action-buttons button {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 12px;
      font-size: 16px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 8px;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: 0.3s;
      text-decoration: none;
      text-align: center;
    }
    
    /* Logout button */
    .logout-form button {
      background: #e74c3c;
      color: white;
    }
    .logout-form button:hover {
      background: #c0392b;
    }

    /* Additional Info/Buttons for Teachers */
    .info-box {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 15px;
        background-color: #e6f7e6; /* Yashilroq fon */
        border: 1px solid #c8e6c9;
        border-radius: 8px;
        color: #2e7d32;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Shaxsiy Kabinet ðŸ‘¤</h1>
    <h2 style="color: #27ae60;"><%= userData.first_name %> <%= userData.last_name %></h2>

    <% if (userData.role === 'admin') { %>
        <div class="info-box" style="background-color: #ffe0b2; color: #ef6c00;">
            <p>Siz Admin roliga egasiz. Boshqaruv Paneliga o'tishingiz mumkin:</p>
            <a href="/admin/dashboard" style="display: block; margin-top: 10px; color: #ef6c00;">Admin Dashboard</a>
        </div>
    <% } %>

    <div class="profile-info">
        <h3>Asosiy ma'lumotlar:</h3>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= userData.email %></p>
        <p><strong>Rol:</strong> <%= userData.role %></p>
        <p><strong>Status:</strong> <%= userData.status %></p>
        <p><strong>Telefon:</strong> <%= userData.phone_number || 'Kiritilmagan' %></p>
        <p><strong>Manzil:</strong> <%= userData.address || 'Kiritilmagan' %></p>
    </div>

    <div class="action-buttons">
        <% if (userData.role === 'admin') { %>
             <a href="/employees/profile/edit" style="background: #2575fc; color: white;">Ma'lumotlarni tahrirlash</a>
        <% } else { %>
            <button disabled style="background: #95a5a6; cursor: not-allowed;" title="Admin ruxsati bilan tahrirlanadi">Ma'lumotlarni tahrirlash (Ruxsat yo'q)</button>
        <% } %>

        <a href="/employees/update-password" style="background: #f1c40f; color: #333;">Parolni o'zgartirish</a> 
    </div>
    
    <div class="info-box">
        <h4>Teacher vazifalari:</h4>
        <p>Bu yerda yaqin orada bo'lib o'tadigan darslar jadvali, o'quvchilar ro'yxati yoki xabarnomalar joylashadi.</p>
    </div>

    <form class="logout-form" action="/employees/logout" method="POST">
      <button type="submit">Tizimdan chiqish (Logout)</button>
    </form>
  </div>
</body>
</html>